\newlabel{fig:observability}{{1}{3}{Three-pillar cloud-native observability architecture. Microservices auto-instrumented via OpenTelemetry emit metrics (Prometheus), logs (Loki), and distributed traces (Tempo), each capturing a distinct dimension of system behaviour. The observability intelligence layer correlates all three signal types for automated anomaly detection, root cause analysis~(RCA), and predictive forecasting}{figure.caption.1}{}}
